<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.5">
<l>perumak kaḷuḷḷavar tamperu māṉai yamararkaṭ</l>
<l>karumai yoḻiyavaṉ ṟāramu tūṭṭiya vappaṉaip</l>
<l>perumai pitaṟṟa vallāraip pitaṟṟumavar kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>varumaiyu mimmaiyu nammai yaḷikkum pirākkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those, see, who rave about those capable of raving about the greatness</l>
<l>of the great lord of those who are among great people, the father who fed</l>
<l>the rare ambrosia that day so that the difficulties of the immortals ended,</l>
<l>are the lords who take care of us in the coming birth and in this one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
